            android:layout_marginBottom="16dp"
            android:fontFamily="@font/comfortaa_bold"
            android:text="Primarily through respiratory droplets when an infected person coughs, sneezes, or talks. It can also spread by touching surfaces contaminated with the virus and then touching the face. Symptoms Common Symptoms: Fever, dry cough, tiredness. Other ."
